{"tid":544012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習總: Order 66 !","createTime":"2018-01-29T05:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:23:27.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0411bcff6136b670586d5e8171e56297ef003ef1","tid":544012,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T05:57:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57751162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57751162&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=dcfbe400\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57751162&h=99532fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57751162</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【大突破】中國科學家成功複製猴子 全球首例靈長類動物<br />\n<br />\n內地官方新華社報道，中國科學家成功複製一對猴子，突破一直無法複製靈長類動物的障礙。<br />\n<br />\n報道指這研究已經登上國際權威學術期刊《細胞》封面。這次中國科學家複製的一對猴子被稱為「中中」和「華華」，基因都是來自一個流產的雌性獼猴胎兒，科學家利用基因編輯，篩選基因相同的細胞，再用移植方法，產生基因相同的胚胎，最後由母猴懷孕出生。<br />\n「中中」比「華華」大10天，兩者除了頭部有少許差異外，這對猴子姐妹外觀上幾乎沒有分別。<br />\n中科院神經所所長蒲慕明表示，研究結果有望為研究診治腦退化症、自閉症等腦疾病帶來希望。<br />\n自從科學家在1996年首次複製羊「多利」以來，科學家先後複製牛、老鼠、貓、狗等動物，但科學家一直認為以現有技術，是無法複製出與人類相近的靈長類動物。"},{"pid":"812c9f27ec491543444191d0bfb459135620745d","tid":544012,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516840504_b4c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516840504_b4c9.jpg&h=57b1b109&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7554b6fa48fa43979b32d4530ba2d0db9888787d","tid":544012,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T05:59:10.000Z","msg":"使乜複雜，中國成十幾億隻"},{"pid":"4df587a865f04502679824397522458f6e0aeec4","tid":544012,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T05:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>使乜複製，中國成十幾億隻</blockquote>"},{"pid":"08544736d2e1627acaa278841e97beb108ef1744","tid":544012,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57751162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57751162&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=dcfbe400\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57751162&h=99532fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57751162</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【大突破】中國科學家成功複製猴子 全球首例靈長類動物<br />\n<br />\n內地官方新華社報道，中國科學家成功複製一對猴子，突破一直無法複製靈長類動物的障礙。<br />\n<br />\n報道指這研究已經登上國際權威學術期刊《細胞》封面。這次中國科學家複製的一對猴子被稱為「中中」和「華華」，基因都是來自一個流產的雌性獼猴胎兒，科學家利用基因編輯，篩選基因相同的細胞，再用移植方法，產生基因相同的胚胎，最後由母猴懷孕出生。<br />\n「中中」比「華華」大10天，兩者除了頭部有少許差異外，這對猴子姐妹外觀上幾乎沒有分別。<br />\n中科院神經所所長蒲慕明表示，研究結果有望為研究診治腦退化症、自閉症等腦疾病帶來希望。<br />\n自從科學家在1996年首次複製羊「多利」以來，科學家先後複製牛、老鼠、貓、狗等動物，<span style=\"color: red;\">但科學家一直認為以現有技術，是無法複製出與人類相近的靈長類動物。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華文媒體又玩語言藝術,吹大支那<br />\n唔係無技術,係道德上西方科學唔容許"},{"pid":"c21754017c2aa3b67e636c6742c8dfd2172bb5b2","tid":544012,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"奇門遁甲"},{"pid":"f1444787a5521a2620f4b7c9af78c62aee7dc1d2","tid":544012,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:13:59.000Z","msg":"將抄襲昇華到另外一個境界"},{"pid":"695b154470ce269871f601d0367fe2d496025429","tid":544012,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d1cf38add6ded3c0a974531277037235a6e5332","tid":544012,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}